{"tid":484172,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打去過格魯吉亞？","createTime":"2017-11-30T00:05:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T04:52:36.000Z","uid":77776,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"801e0102fceddd775a917c37b1a34c7ed0f6499b","tid":484172,"uid":77776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T00:05:02.000Z","msg":"想問下果邊風景如何？洗費點架？"},{"pid":"7d108b530d7a96ae39c4244cc6d7d6032b2364cb","tid":484172,"uid":33777,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T05:14:59.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4bd00355cb84df089f1c404e49be69b29559f460","tid":484172,"uid":51744,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T07:50:36.000Z","msg":"上年去過第比利斯，首都整得幾好，個人覺得地方幾靚<br />\n<br />\n物價大概係香港一半，但有＊嘅酒店就國際價錢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/155000_da9dfcbd72a09e8456a8a95feacbe219.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F155000_da9dfcbd72a09e8456a8a95feacbe219.jpg&h=8ba774d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/155003_41f8b4ff8b1117d540b5bf3c2902e628.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F155003_41f8b4ff8b1117d540b5bf3c2902e628.jpg&h=7878d99c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/155006_5bb4d7a864548d72349292a921007b54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F155006_5bb4d7a864548d72349292a921007b54.jpg&h=e6cc9e72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/155009_a9d96141f4f56360f26c3a7d4ceddb58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F155009_a9d96141f4f56360f26c3a7d4ceddb58.jpg&h=3a19b8c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/155011_9c6d5c09188450ab59e649c6a547658b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F155011_9c6d5c09188450ab59e649c6a547658b.jpg&h=60ebefd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/155012_4d99ce203536b9b3c356c312b6c6cdf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F155012_4d99ce203536b9b3c356c312b6c6cdf8.jpg&h=b8f64080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/155013_b085d0ff05ebb2e03b4da247183d08c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F155013_b085d0ff05ebb2e03b4da247183d08c2.jpg&h=7af3a0d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7d14b0530c23d0f6ebb54fdb584a998fe57f4d8","tid":484172,"uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T08:02:19.000Z","msg":"mestia行山無得頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過住宿麻麻，但要平都唔好要咁多"},{"pid":"0d9ebbe16959a667642572cf801f94fc34e01ec2","tid":484172,"uid":77776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:35:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似好正"},{"pid":"0ae6e41f821b71c393e2981065cc6e19acb4c626","tid":484172,"uid":155601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:12:57.000Z","msg":"城市之間交通如何"},{"pid":"5ad8205755382b9209df26076db835ed43d77567","tid":484172,"uid":93483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:39:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>城市之間交通如何</blockquote><br />\n搭小巴 ( 九成時間) 佢地叫做Matsuka (唔知有無串錯) <br />\n行山同埋教堂真係正到震"},{"pid":"6fa7b44df503172575266598e44cb77ce6639551","tid":484172,"uid":93483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:40:10.000Z","msg":"最好去埋Armenia"},{"pid":"569fba9f4da99875a1665e000030e04354f254f6","tid":484172,"uid":51744,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:10:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>城市之間交通如何</blockquote><br />\n搭小巴 ( 九成時間) 佢地叫做Matsuka (唔知有無串錯) <br />\n行山同埋教堂真係正到震</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMarshrutka<br />\n<br />\n坐一次由Tbilisi去Batumi，港幣六十幾，坐足八粒鐘。坐火車頭等五粒鐘，大概一舊水。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/01/011011_657e402d08cf77aa6b695868baf252c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2F011011_657e402d08cf77aa6b695868baf252c3.jpg&h=e0a136ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/01/011014_5b3a8a0d003fd7c09c351e2d8a7b656a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2F011014_5b3a8a0d003fd7c09c351e2d8a7b656a.jpg&h=0ce4ffe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/01/011015_d4fedbdba64688174306d91015ddfc7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2F011015_d4fedbdba64688174306d91015ddfc7d.jpg&h=421d59d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/01/011017_12338b70302fbf1e0728e094173d5673.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2F011017_12338b70302fbf1e0728e094173d5673.jpg&h=930ce952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/01/011018_fcfaa3bc12d1715c74601019e1c4b3fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2F011018_fcfaa3bc12d1715c74601019e1c4b3fc.jpg&h=28238b3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/01/011020_5bba68e1a0144b3809b07a4f6e52a4de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2F011020_5bba68e1a0144b3809b07a4f6e52a4de.jpg&h=dec3b926&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd984f582f5138ede000b5555019a9e0fc23009b","tid":484172,"uid":77776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T19:27:45.000Z","msg":"洗費多少？"},{"pid":"1d759461bf9dbbaea2997f25c329668996d48876","tid":484172,"uid":51744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T20:04:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗費多少？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇時辰，五月頭住Hilton 一晚包晚餐再加免費升等套房八舊。街邊士多大枝玻璃樽可樂，三蚊港幣。市中心較高檔餐廳，三個course加aperitif 大概一舊。"},{"pid":"c9b0e383754506ac4fc281d15adfc6ffe38f5635","tid":484172,"uid":155601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T20:51:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去埋亞美尼亞同阿塞拜疆難唔難"},{"pid":"e340849cabdfe461059c271e7f33cb297940d276","tid":484172,"uid":77776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T22:57:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>洗費多少？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇時辰，五月頭住Hilton 一晚包晚餐再加免費升等套房八舊。街邊士多大枝玻璃樽可樂，三蚊港幣。市中心較高檔餐廳，三個course加aperitif 大概一舊。</blockquote><br />\n好似都ok.果時巴打剩係玩格魯吉亞？"},{"pid":"b00a1a3d45794202f438c2d0454dcc674d579d48","tid":484172,"uid":66954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T06:28:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去埋亞美尼亞同阿塞拜疆難唔難</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n首都同首都之間有火車，去唔難<br />\n但阿塞拜疆要簽證"},{"pid":"ac9f21664ff3f658b9e4dd2fe116e2bcdec2ccb7","tid":484172,"uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T06:30:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗費多少？</blockquote><br />\n平有平玩<br />\n大把hostel, guesthouse"},{"pid":"176a60f340902ce4bc6ccbb944168ab43e1fbcb0","tid":484172,"uid":10616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T06:44:08.000Z","msg":"想十二月尾去獨遊<br />\n飛機大概要搭幾耐？<br />\n治安如何？"},{"pid":"c51bcf9d79c337692cc2758f366bbde37374bfb1","tid":484172,"uid":45749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T06:52:08.000Z","msg":"用俄文 英文溝唔溝通到？"},{"pid":"33324628e6e17515e51d228459ae116fb176c979","tid":484172,"uid":14566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:09:58.000Z","msg":"真心冷門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俄羅斯能源走廊"},{"pid":"dec157dd2cf995e7853e7513dea4d1f78eef9ddd","tid":484172,"uid":48958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:13:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心冷門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俄羅斯能源走廊</blockquote><br />\n阿塞拜疆仲冷門，因為簽證又煩又貴"},{"pid":"18838acdf5dc3fc28af3e72f19591e19c5e4f61a","tid":484172,"uid":51744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:31:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>洗費多少？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇時辰，五月頭住Hilton 一晚包晚餐再加免費升等套房八舊。街邊士多大枝玻璃樽可樂，三蚊港幣。市中心較高檔餐廳，三個course加aperitif 大概一舊。</blockquote><br />\n好似都ok.果時巴打剩係玩格魯吉亞？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，因為只有短短五、六日時間。"},{"pid":"1da3912ff4c8e4c831b659e037e6f8a597ab67d9","tid":484172,"uid":51744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:32:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想十二月尾去獨遊<br />\n飛機大概要搭幾耐？<br />\n治安如何？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n治安OK，夜晚十一點幾係市中心逛都燈火通明"},{"pid":"d82432b06a69e7bf0314464a19602d4ad1905865","tid":484172,"uid":51744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:37:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真心冷門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俄羅斯能源走廊</blockquote><br />\n阿塞拜疆仲冷門，因為簽證又煩又貴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點又煩又貴？  阿塞拜疆已經係最易申請嘅簽證。  人家出咗EVISA，上網俾廿幾蚊美金攪掂。詳情自己睇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://evisa.gov.az/en/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fevisa.gov.az%2Fen%2F&d=iVdJo81XXU2rHDVppMyVTE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=1db67513\" target=\"_blank\">https://evisa.gov.az/en/</a>"},{"pid":"af16910d3aa16c926700883af42589badc6dfdcf","tid":484172,"uid":51744,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:40:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用俄文 英文溝唔溝通到？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你識俄文就最好，不過格魯吉亞人唔太鍾意俄人。  英文一般旅遊地方OK，我見唔到有幾大困難。"},{"pid":"75b9747b0652258a6def6f143ea90a56d8754a47","tid":484172,"uid":55923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T14:36:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真心冷門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俄羅斯能源走廊</blockquote><br />\n阿塞拜疆仲冷門，因為簽證又煩又貴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點又煩又貴？  阿塞拜疆已經係最易申請嘅簽證。  人家出咗EVISA，上網俾廿幾蚊美金攪掂。詳情自己睇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://evisa.gov.az/en/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fevisa.gov.az%2Fen%2F&d=iVdJo81XXU2rHDVppMyVTE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=1db67513\" target=\"_blank\">https://evisa.gov.az/en/</a></blockquote><br />\n煩在Armenia 同Azerbaijan 都係single entry visa,<br />\nGeorgia 嘅evisa就係30-day multiple entry, 可以用嚟做transport hub一次去哂南高加索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8162f9d0622ab473ebe83a0c098a51a69aa70d98","tid":484172,"uid":10434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T15:20:19.000Z","msg":"兩個月前去，主要去酒莊參觀<br />\n<br />\n簽證好方便，英文可以溝通到（都叫可以），佢地好唔鍾意俄佬係真既，首都入夜都仲燈火通明<br />\n<br />\n查實格魯吉亞人都幾排外，做生意上尼都幾奸，冇想像中咁「未與世界接軌」<br />\n<br />\n等巴打遊記，因為我果時留kakheti多"}]}